      <title>波音法官在认罪协议裁决前寻求更多信息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/boeing-judge-seeks-more-information-before-plea-deal-ruling</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名德克萨斯州联邦法官正在审查波音公司与美国检察官就两起致命坠机事件达成的认罪协议，他要求提供更多信息以确定是否应该批准该协议，包括多元化和包容性承诺将如何影响外部监察员的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-15/boeing-judge-seeks-more-information-before-plea-deal-ruling</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Oct 2024 20:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
